  <summary>4/30/2015--Introduced.
VA Employee Fairness Act of 2015

Repeals provisions excluding any matter or question concerning professional conduct or competence, peer review, or the establishment, determination, or adjustment of employee compensation from the applicability of collective bargaining rights for Veterans Health Administration employees.</summary>
